* Speech to text description:
I created an html page that contains two buttons, the first with Arabic written on it,to convert Arabic speech into Arabic text and written on it 
in English to convert English speech into English text.  The size of the texts on the page and the color of the button on the page. When you press 
one of the buttons,the listining text will appear and the speech will begin to be heard. When the stoped text appears, the text will appear as written after text:

* Description of ESP32 operation:
After downloading the ESP32 library on the Arduino, and if the ESP32 piece is wired with the device, we run the blink code so that the blue light appears
in a frequency on the device.  Blue frequency on the device emulator
